        <h2>Volleyball-Specific Planning</h2>
        <p>Volleyball teams typically have 12-18 players. The smaller size means you can invest more per player in personal touches, gifts, and custom centerpieces.</p>

        <h3>Volleyball Decor Themes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Net Results</strong> — Court-themed with netting accents and volleyball graphics</li>
          <li><strong>Dig Pink</strong> — Breast cancer awareness themed (if your team participated)</li>
          <li><strong>Spike It!</strong> — High-energy theme with action photo displays</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="product-note">
          <p><strong>🏐 Volleyball Centerpieces:</strong> Custom 3D printed volleyball centerpieces (8") in your team's colors with personalization options. Classic volleyball panel design with a textured surface. Perfect for banquet tables, the awards table, or as senior night keepsakes.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/volleyball-banquet-table-centerpiece-8-volleyball" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">View Volleyball Centerpieces →</a>
        </div>

        <h2>Volleyball Award Ideas</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Team MVP</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Offensive Player of the Year</strong> — Kills leader</li>
          <li><strong>Defensive Player of the Year</strong> — Digs leader</li>
          <li><strong>Setter of the Year</strong> — Assists leader</li>
          <li><strong>Serve Ace Award</strong> — Serving percentage leader</li>
          <li><strong>Most Improved Player</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Team Spirit Award</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Senior Night for Volleyball</h2>
        <p>Volleyball senior night is typically the last home match. Many programs decorate the gym with senior banners, balloons, and team photos. Consider custom volleyball centerpieces for the senior table at the post-match reception or end-of-season banquet.</p>

        <p><a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-outline">Full Banquet Guide →</a> <a href="/senior-night/" class="btn btn-outline">Senior Night Guide →</a></p>
